{"tid":2113920,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"上海 階級","createTime":"2020-07-18T12:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T12:13:40.000Z","uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97af68ad555344716400ceb8786203047f00c9f5","tid":2113920,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"上海市把所有市民，依照財力分成五類十二等人，你是下等人，你的孩子也是下等人，就算小學在你家旁邊， 你的孩子一樣就沒有相同的入學權利，文革雖然過，但黑五類的階級永遠存在。<br />\n<br />\n有八十五個家庭聯名控訴後，反被公安威脅並暴力相向，不禁哭訴並要問政府，是誰給你的權利?<br />\n<br />\n很簡單，黨給的啊！不然你想怎樣呢？爭獨立嗎？你的需求，我早給你否決了，懂?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/d3fdsZaBwvzwNS322kf34Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fd3fdsZaBwvzwNS322kf34Q&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=2f401a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/d3fdsZaBwvzwNS322kf34Q</a>"}]}